### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ==========================================
### 1. GOAL & TASK MANAGEMENT
### ==========================================

### Get All Tasks (Should see seed data)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Accept: application/json

### Create a New Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test the API manually",
  "goalId": 1,
  "estimatedMinutes": 45,
  "dueDatetime": "2026-12-31T23:59:00"
}

### ==========================================
### 2. TASK ACTIVITY LOGS (NEW FEATURE)
### ==========================================

### Get Timeline for Seed Task #1 (Expect 2 logs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/1/activity
Accept: application/json

### ==========================================
### 3. TASK REVIEW FLOW
### ==========================================

### Get Tasks Needing Review (Seed Task #3 might appear here after scheduler runs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/review
Accept: application/json

### Review a Task (Mark Task #4 as RESUMED)
# Note: You might need to change ID 4 to an actual task ID that needs review
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/4/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision": "RESUME",
  "note": "Feeling better now"
}

### ==========================================
### 4. TIME BLOCKING
### ==========================================

### Create Time Block for Task #2
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/2/time-blocks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-02-02T14:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-02-02T16:00:00"
}

